snippet.title: Cat jump
snippet.description:
The addictive arcade game, Cat Jump! Will you challenge the highest record?
Anyone can play this addictive and aggravating game, Cat Jump easily.
Let's reach the highest score with your cute cat by avoiding the aggressive obstacle! jump! jump!

Featuring the game
- A simple touch operation!
- A fun score competition with your friend by your control!
- A fun of collecting the cute and various cat!
- Helping your concentration, a quick reaction, a speedy control, and an improvement of broad outlook!

Just play! Have fun! Enjoy the game!
